PRIVACY COMMITMENT:
This software is designed with privacy-first principles:
- No data collection
- No external servers
- All processing happens locally on the user's device
- No user tracking or analytics
- Complete transparency in data handling

AI MODELS:
This software uses the following open-source AI models:
- Whisper (OpenAI) - Speech Recognition
- TinyLlama, Qwen, Phi-2 (HuggingFace) - Chat AI
- ONNX Models (Microsoft) - Vision Processing
- MediaPipe (Google) - Gesture Recognition
- TensorFlow Lite (Google) - Language Processing

All AI models are used in accordance with their respective licenses.

